\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
L^{A}\cong\bbnum 1+(\bbnum 1\rightarrow A\times L^{A})\quad.\label{eq:fixpoint-type-equation-for-oncall-list}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

We may write the same equation using a recursion scheme 
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

