\begin_inset Formula 
\[
L^{A}\cong F^{A,L^{A}}\quad,\quad\quad F^{A,R}\triangleq\bbnum 1+(\bbnum 1\rightarrow A\times R)\quad.
\]

\end_inset

A solution of this fixpoint equation can be visualized (non-rigorously)
